@b{OX_DATA}, @b{OX_COMMAND}, @b{OX_SYNC_BALL}.
Usually @b{OX_COMMAND} and @b{OX_SYNC_BALL} are
sent implicitly with high level operations, but
these functions are prepared to send these data explicitly.

@item
